ars of working - literally around the globe - for corporates, fund managers and as finance academic. In his last role his research has focused on investment decisions, and during 2012 he interviewed 34 fund managers in Istanbul, London, New York and Melbourne. He blends rich understanding of finance theory and practic.</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="588"><subfield code="a">Print version record.</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="596"><subfield code="a">44</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2="0" tag="650"><subfield code="a">Banks and banking.</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2="0" tag="650"><subfield code="a">Financial institutions</subfield><subfield code="x">Law and legislation.</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2="0" tag="650"><subfield code="a">Finance</subfield><subfield code="x">Corrupt practices.</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1="4" ind2="0" tag="856"><subfield code="3">University of Alberta Access</subfield><subfield code="u">http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&amp;scope=site&amp;db=nlebk&amp;db=nlabk&amp;AN=821569</subfield><subfield code="z">(Single User Access)</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="949"><subfield code="h">UAIN</subfield><subfield code="z">PDAOWNED</subfield></datafield><datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="926"><subfield code="a">Internet Access</subfield><subfield code="w">LC</subfield><subfield code="c">1</subfield><subfield code="i">6772330-1001</subfield><subfield code="l">INTERNET</subfield><subfield code="m">UAINTERNET</subfield><subfield code="r">Y</subfield><subfield code="s">Y</subfield><subfield code="t">E-RESOURCE</subfield><subfield code="u">1/10/2015</subfield><subfield code="x">E-BOOK</subfield><subfield code="z">PDAOWNED</subfield></datafield></record>